_sText:
Hello everyone!

This is new remake for CS:S of one popular BF3 map "Noshahr Canals". I worked with this map around nine weeks and she still not finished, now only in beta stage, maybe 90% of the map is now completed. The reason why I upload not completed map now is because in close future I have not chance to finish her. I know that on map exist a few non critical bugs which I planning to fix when again resume work on this map.

Gameplay note: you can use containers doors to rise the roofs of containers, I just not created a proper sign which can mark this. In archive you also will find manually tuned bots .nav file.

Good game!
